<br>
 The Assassin followed Hermes, watching him merge, and the identicals emerge. Down from the tree the Amazon dropped, drawing her sword.<br>
<br>
 A loud war cry was let out.. not as a summon of war. But a warning to the other Amazons. <br>
<br>
 The assassin had a anger for the male gods on Olympus.. and this wouldn't be tolerated from her. <br>
<br>
 Playing games in Amazon territory was not wise, but ignorance.<br>
<br>
 The sword was held out, as Dawn walked along..her senses keeping tabs on all 10 of the hermes and the lioness. A low growl rumbling from her throat.<br>
<br>
