<br>
::Not good.  I came here to escape from my duties and worries, and I seem to have met each and everyone head on.<br>
<br>
Not knowing what to do next.  Hermes went with instinct.  Quickly dropping to one knee, in proper respect, Hermes paid tribute to Hera.<br>
<br>
Keeping his head down, knowing that he was not allowed to look up without given the permission to do so.  Hermes replied.<br>
<br>
::Queen Hera, I am but a humble messenger.  My speed is but a crawl in comparison to your grace.  I only hope that I will not disgrace, but to do you honor.<br>
